Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.user

Class UserProjectCreationDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.user.UserProjectCreationDto
public class UserProjectCreationDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for creating a user project. This class encapsulates all necessary information to create a new project associated with a user, including project details, skills required, and privacy settings.
